00:04:07.170 --> 00:04:10.740
it became serious,

00:04:10.950 --> 00:04:14.860
but is that a proof of liking?

00:04:16.660 --> 00:04:22.900
It's because you're the one who misunderstood it;

00:04:22.980 --> 00:04:28.730
An explosive irony.

